  "commit_message": "perf: content-check modified manifests and fall back to the current lockfile on the repeat-install fast path (pacquet + pnpm) (#12315)\n\n## Why\n\nOn [benchmarks.vlt.sh](https://benchmarks.vlt.sh/) (2026-06-10 run, pacquet 0.11.2), pacquet ranked **8th–9th of 10** in every `lockfile+node_modules` variation — slower than pnpm, npm, yarn and vlt — e.g. astro: pacquet 936 ms vs pnpm 502 ms; babylon: pacquet 9.08 s vs pnpm 0.85 s. It also trailed vlt/npm in the `node_modules` and `cache+node_modules` v",
